Git Log Aliases

View commit history in various formats.

$ [prgm]git ls[/prgm]                    # List recent commits (oneline, colored)
$ [prgm]git ll[/prgm]                    # List commits with file changes
$ [prgm]git lsd[/prgm]                   # Graph view with stats

$ [prgm]git dlt[/prgm]                   # Git log, using difftastic
$ [prgm]git dld[/prgm]                   # Git log, using delta
$ [prgm]git dlr[/prgm]                   # Git log, using diffr
